{"id":"9a41d5df-c34d-4c1e-8a03-9b2271b3372f","name":"Nice Nature (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Mrsdu5XY4Hc7z2D522dIK.webp\" style=\"width: 536px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br>─── 🥉 ───</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Don't expect much from her. This Umamusume is super cynical.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>An Umamusume of humble background with a penchant for being pessimistic. She tends to think of herself as a supporting character, and this causes her to shy away from high expectations—this sometimes leads to imperfect performances. She has quite the knack for cooking and cleaning due to her working-class upbringing, and does so whenever she has time. She's something of a familiar face among the seniors in her town.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 169, 89);\"><strong><br><em>\"Yup, I'm happy with a third place—it's all an extra like me can ask for.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/K4fq1inTSIo3K53KYF2_W.webp\" style=\"width: 446px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">— — — — — — ❖ III ❖ — — — — — —</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 169, 89);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 169, 89);\"><strong><br><em>1) Finishing 3rd</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 169, 89);\"><strong><em>2) The family bar</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 169, 89);\"><strong><em>3) Karaoke</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 169, 89);\"><strong><em>4) You're sick</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 169, 89);\"><strong><em>5) Winning</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 169, 89);\"><strong><em>6) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/p6iK_GX9ROO4ZjzmohEvd.webp\" style=\"width: 410px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">— — — — — — ❖ III ❖ — — — — — —</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Another umawife. She's such a cutie.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">— — — — — — ❖ III ❖ — — — — — —</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/H8Qm9/status/1982044558625226826/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@H8Qm9</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/135607125\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/138071088\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/LeonMandala/status/1955761414804734279/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"STNKuUxUrlhA07YYsnPVZ.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2618,"messages":56348,"created_at":"2025-12-30T18:50:00.868959+00:00"}